Name: Theresia LavergneTitle: ProfessorSpecialization: PoultryE-mail: Department: School of Animal SciencesOrganization: LSU AgCenterAddress 1: 105 J.B. Francioni, LSUAddress 2: Baton Rouge, LA 70803 - 4210Phone Number: (225) 578-2473Fax Number: (225) 578-3604





Education/Training1994 - 1997      
Louisiana State University, Baton Rouge, LA
Doctor of Philosophy (Non-ruminant nutrition)1992 - 1993
Mississippi State University, Mississippi State, MS
Master of Science (Non-ruminant nutrition)1989 - 1992
Auburn University, Auburn, AL
Bachelor of Science (Animal and Dairy Sciences)

Areas of Specialization/ResearchPoultry nutrition, management, and litter management.

Professional ExperienceJanuary 2013 - presentProfessor, Poultry (90% Extension, 10% Research), LSU AgCenter, Baton Rouge, LA July 2011 - January 2013Professor, Poultry (100% Extension), LSU AgCenter, Baton Rouge, LA
July 2005 - June 2011Associate Professor, Poultry (100% Extension), LSU AgCenter, Baton Rouge, LA
January 2000 - June 2005Assistant Professor, Poultry (100% Extension), LSU AgCenter, Baton Rouge, LA
January 1998 - December 1999Swine Technical Service Manager, Land O’ Lakes, Inc., Fort Dodge, IA

August 1997 - December 1997Instructor, Department of Agriculture, Austin Peay State University, Clarksville, TN

Awards/GrantsAwards and Honors2001 Louisiana Poultry Federation “President’s Award”2003 Louisiana Poultry Federation “President’s Award”2004 Louisiana Poultry Federation “President’s Award”2004 4-H Specialist Award2004 Louisiana Poultry Federation “Man of the Year” Award2004 LSU AgCenter Extension Excellence Award2005 LSU AgCenter Louisiana Agriculture Service Award2006 Louisiana Poultry Federation “President’s Award”2006 Extension Recognition Award (from the PSA extension workshop committee)2008 LSU AgCenter Internal Leadership Program (completion award)2008 Epsilon Sigma Phi Early Career Award2010 Louisiana Poultry Federation “President’s Award”2011 Poultry Science Association Appreciation Award for Service as an At-Large Director2011 Louisiana Poultry Federation “Helping Hand Award”2011 JCEP Excellence in Teamwork Award (for AgMagic)2012 Epsilon Sigma Phi Mid-Career Award2013 Louisiana Poultry Federation “Helping Hand Award”2014 LSU AgCenter Ag Leadership Class XIII Graduate2015 Louisiana Poultry Seminar – Recognition Award
